    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公元848 年。世界被谎言与欲望所淹没。傲慢的 富人控制着普通人的命运。唯有依附贵族的恩惠，才能找到可怜的庇护所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角 Envet Nokt 在失去一切后，为了在这个腐败的世界生存，走上了偷窃的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您必须学会在黑暗中躲藏，在光明中警惕。揭开别人家园及其居民的黑暗秘密，在阳光下找到自己的一席之地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188360/extras/27b745e87bcb14fa998af69920c7e209.poster.avif?t=1768675020\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188360/extras/27b745e87bcb14fa998af69920c7e209.webm?t=1768675020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188360/extras/27b745e87bcb14fa998af69920c7e209.mp4?t=1768675020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等距隐形-RPG。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 独特的破解机制。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188360/extras/5ba279ad487a46333d7f562e8f2e9567.poster.avif?t=1768675020\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188360/extras/5ba279ad487a46333d7f562e8f2e9567.webm?t=1768675020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188360/extras/5ba279ad487a46333d7f562e8f2e9567.mp4?t=1768675020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深思熟虑您的一举一动，以达到目的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >躲在阴暗处，因为黑暗是您最好的朋友。然而，别忘了它並不如您想像的那么安全。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 细腻的世界和意想不到的曲折情节。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 没有杀戮，只有隐身的技巧才能帮助您通过 Envet Nokt 之路。</p></li></ul>",
